<div class="story">
<p>Tuckahoe is an ocean to sound community with 40 lots on the ocean side of Rte 12 and 44 lots on the soundside and most of the lots are large enough to accommodate an in ground pool. The Home Owners Association manages to keep the association fee down even after having to maintain the private roads, the community pool, a tennis court and the ocean and sound accesses. The ocean access has a minimal amount of parking for owners on the westside. Tuakahoe is located in the southern end of Duck just north of the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/bias-shores.asp" title="Bias Shores">Bias Shores</a> and south of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/sea-hawk-south.asp" title="Sea Hawk South">Sea Hawk South</a>. </p>
